title: INTERVIEW: Diny Fielder-van Kleeff & Rachael Marshall - Vaccine Control Group
cleaned_text:
In this episode of the Patrick Henningsen Show on TNT Radio which aired on February 10, 2023, Patrick speaks with Diny Fielder-van Kleeff & Rachael Marshall from the Vaccine Control Group, an independent, worldwide, long-term study group tracking the health outcomes of the SARS-CoV-2 vaccine-free. A citizen-led initiative, it’s open to anyone who has chosen not to be jabbed. A truly incredible story, and a great resource for anyone who wants to get on board. Listen:
